race.description: The Adviser Collective Country Boosted Handicap
race.comment: INVINCIBLE WHIP (2) only the one win from ten starts and finds a winnable race third-up. Senior rider takes the reins and desperate for the 1200m here after chipping away late when fifth over 1000m at Port Macquarie. YES YES BOSS (8) relished the class drop when a slick on pace winner over 1000m at Muswellbrook. Up in class and sure to be about the minor money again. STIORRA (9) deep into her prep and stretches out to the 1200m for the first time. Was fair late when fourth over 1000m at Muswellbrook. Top three prospect. ENSIGN PARKER (1) drops a few grades for this after sitting on the speed when a respectable sixth over 1200m at Scone in C3 grade. One for the exotics.
